sequenceDiagram
    participant CN as Container Node (ESP32-S3)
    participant SD as SD Card (Local Backup)
    participant GN as Gateway Node (SIM800L)
    participant EMQX as EMQX Serverless Broker
    participant BE as Backend Services
    participant DB as Neon PostgreSQL DB
    participant FE as Frontend Application

    note over CN,GN: Edge Network (Isolated Trailer)
    loop Every 2500ms
        CN->>CN: Read Sensors (I2C/Analog)<br/>AHT10, BMP180, MPU6050, MQ2
        
        CN->>SD: appendLogCsv()<br/>Log Raw Telemetry Locally
        SD-->>CN: status: sdOk
        
        CN->>GN: WiFi ESP-NOW Broadcast<br/>[CargoPacket] struct
    end
    
    note over GN,EMQX: Uplink Backhaul (Cellular TLS)
    loop Async Event Driven
        GN->>GN: Receive ESP-NOW Packet
        GN->>GN: Read Serial GPS (NMEA)<br/>Acquire Lat/Lon/Speed & Time
        
        note right of GN: Construct JSON Payload
        GN->>GN: Merge Sensor Data + GPS Fix
        
        GN->>EMQX: SSLClient MQTTS Publish (Port 8883)<br/>topic: tenant/demo/truck/.../telemetry
        EMQX-->>GN: PUBACK (if QoS > 0)
    end
    
    note over EMQX,DB: Cloud Processing Pipeline
    loop Message Routing
        EMQX->>BE: MQTT Subscription / Webhook<br/>Deliver JSON Payload
        
        BE->>BE: Validate Token/Topic & Map Schema
        BE->>BE: Evaluate Conditions for Alerts<br/>(e.g., Gas Alert, Shock Threshold)
        
        BE->>DB: ORM Insert/Update Query<br/>Write telemetry & update states
        DB-->>BE: Query Ack
    end
    
    note over BE,FE: Presentation App
    loop Client View
        FE->>BE: HTTP GET /api/telemetry/latest <br/>or <br/>WebSocket Upgrade
        BE->>DB: Fetch Recent History
        DB-->>BE: Result Rows
        BE-->>FE: JSON Response / WS Stream
        FE->>FE: Update Dashboard Charts/Map
    end
